<del rend="strikethrough"> Alſo wem </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_401_r1l16">Alſo <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr etwen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> </ab>
